				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I do like the merging idea, but it would be a bit hard to implement I imagine.
<br />

<br />
Sort of off topic, but I wouldn't mind an Elemental Mastery Form either heh.  Simply make it a combination of every single form, with all the forms at concurrent levels as pre-requisites.  i.e. Elemental Mastery Form 1 requires Water/Earth/Air/Fire all at level 1, and gives all the benefits of them simultaneously.  Level 2 requires all the forms at level 2, and so on.
<br />

<br />
Might be a bit overpowered, but then you have to factor in the AA cost of doing such a thing.  Mastery form 3 would take a whopping 90 AA points in total to achieve.  I think the Levitate portion would have to be removed though, as it wouldn't let us use the form in certain zones.
<br />

<br />
But, I suppose Sony wouldn't go for this idea.  After all, all the elemental forms must share the same timer for this very reason.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=212730" target="_blank" class="postlink">Nirrudn Ak`Lmar</a>,
